## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of the impact of caregiving on personal well-being. The information is limited to the perspectives and studies cited in the sources, and further research may be required for a comprehensive understanding. Additionally, the data is up to date as of October 2023, and newer studies or insights may not be included.